headline: ZBH Q2 Deep Dive: New Product Launches and M&A Drive Guidance Upgrades
summary: Medical device company Zimmer Biomet (NYSE:ZBH) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 7% year on year to $2.08 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.07 per share was 4.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
